 arguments path uses NativeJavaClass, it may not be needed. There's a potential issue since the Native Image test catches an error but still returns successfully. I see the documentation mentions a pattern of returning after a catch, while our method just ends without a return. I think I need to ensure my final response is concise before any git diff.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_01fc0e625fba6484016a2736cf402c8190b234e99a78bc37dd\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqJzbliII05lrFnpCB1fgEYuEIQhixryYqdmfj_OXX-VNCkI8nur9bH_YUNEurGd7bLFaiudv6yA0_wjjdija01izoHzq2tZdTQVRYs3YrBkPL57u7ihYiSEDYXNtKh_hSaJAmwGcquLjMpC7867z9AQbSyILLBQPyOP7s-XrIfSE0YOCSlej2uwD4D5jZC-fl6PTgOgcC6Wnxfdm4BEkfyzMAOF-LtNhobHzYDH217MwByHC1Skz7kJyyoSEmVtQn9F6Uqh2xeiHWN1QFOXnW4Wnss26nOo6y-vEVvvt2JVohxXBYwTYtHhZyUpipu-IWGsHqLmbAOb-O4Kov7iRgMFy7StKVcb_j_Po9RELjTPbEKbciLWFNPIfAG-teglWF1TZfboZjryuTUU1XjyixeiJXjCgHFdt-GeMCM1X3MAxqCJ6nkqVkJrDwfu76RNLUhVGxevPdf5NUyjMbTeXedwt5NJdX_h-KYqz5dGx3yIQD6GPldtib4VL7XS7_fIt4xnCEI6OVlMQ8JrS_IhcKzXRCwiUODVlzxyriC-cUr6-BgkH4481ECYjO4rYB141kC34IL3tuzL6BM0r03KKxMPBlRMJ81QrNGJDBm06ZghNeoZy-FXeWHi89323l2V-wAcGcihlYV5hw3BljPcjkeQvnl3tYrDknMMW-4pYp4xgjq2GK8_hVEcplSRYdt8OImsQBNKDb1MiLjjZCLSxL_TdEmEcqHn2i25w2ZbYrzOAO8e_DNccUvnBQx9m57-rCNnierOsNh2rjgZB6oKB0sXV8L-XGhsDcQsHTaIENu8J3ItrGpENoq6VGamwI7JOx7s6KqJHWo9a4Iqe1rWSP60hzskMG_1D6zSROczOUo5NBo3dhRtSYF9EiuSlBN-Wg1i45jQ_BxV4surpf9Wcd-59TEChOebIj53Hv8BupX8K-AbtAd5dwtjsBl2Z9EZLRTEZiXHvq_GsWezQEwLRmLhF_F1bbAhbvM9ge9kS1D9G_AAFkqmIyrc_WyE1zsuA24GrTj9OV4J4BajhMGigWY3JnlWZROowCUW3o0ARuSwkA8A86uLkrpKYKd4LCwQFiovAEhdRtZ6gG7eQh2mh5UsUYNpT4L4FssgQDSIZ__I3_1HKsFkd0Wi81CZ0LqVEyFhrBoo-VUtooJJ5LjjKdiNYKqa8pI0-PwFddidpCwnwcndqszs0Pufae3xp74mlnUXfqfzD1Zl86w_tYvV9rzeVt_nGdQrh2K8Bv1vNWRU6RMPawF1wMP_Q46eDXF5MUGlFAvKIJ9zOW0InmX9-D2xaRRY2F13mkggROXatyDNKduXr4n2gZWgMzd22KCeUT2CH8p6H0w6cRNyEMLh5mGFdJhXVuGzJnnvoNJVw-DBYjRrf481d3zhYohc8-CnKEquKjl3-vgdQ7mc86iazdmpJ2NVMJRBZgnG_FSC1gi08GK37iLj23OHdu0YJ1W0e1gYjc6Kr_rkv1cJ